Ningbo Home of Staff

Ningbo/ China

   Size/ 104,000 m²
   Competition/ 1st prize, invited international competition 2013
   Status/ Construction 2014–2018
   Client/ Ningbo Labour Union/ City of Ningbo
   Local architect/ NADI (Ningbo Architecture Design Institute)
   Local landscape Architect/ NUCI (Ningbo Union Construction Design
   Institute)
   Photo/ Marc Goodwin
   Share on Facebook Share on LinkedIn

   The Home of Staff has an eclectic mix of functions, split across two
   separate buildings and linked by a landscape park stretching over 500m.
   The Ningbo Labour Union sees the complex as a second home for the
   members they represent. It provides support, health, education, and
   leisure facilities for almost 3 million members. It also contains arts
   and performance area, sports facilities and offices – all built on a
   base of commercial retail and exhibition space.
   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_sketch-organization-2-colour-1170x
   831.jpg]

The Home of Staff entails a series of stepped building volumes that are
linked by a landscape, which rises from a central public park to become
accessible green roof terraces.

   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_Aerial-April-18_02-1170x877.jpg]
   [SHL_Ningbo_HOS_NearCompletion_03_MarcGoodwin-1170x728.jpg]
   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_right-wing-1170x702.jpg]

From the air, the volumes appear like a pixelated image, which rises up at
each end and form two individual buildings that are connected by a sunken
walkway and a series of park pavilions.

   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_Aerial-April-18_01-1170x877.jpg]
   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_interior-379x280.jpg]

The cultural functions of the building include a 3-screen cinema, 1,200-seat
performing arts venue, exhibition hall, Union Staff arts club and service
centre, and training facilities.

   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_pool-view-379x280.jpg]

   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_ground-floor-view-e1456922576645-1
   170x506.jpg]
   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_updated-aerial-1170x428.jpg]
   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_drone-image-1170x652.jpg]

The project sits at the centre of Ningbo New East Town on the edge of an
ecological wetland area forming the new cultural hub of the city.

   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_drone-image-4-1170x1560.jpg]
   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_drone-image-3-1170x658.jpg]

   IFRAME: https://player.vimeo.com/video/178461990

   [SHL_Architects_Ningbo-Home-of-Staff_street-view-1170x785.jpg]
   [SHL_Ningbo_HOS_NearCompletion_04_MarcGoodwin-1170x658.jpg]

related projects/

   [SHL_NingboDaily_Near_Completion_External_01_MarcGoodwin-380x260.jpg]

Ningbo Daily Newspaper Group HQ

   Ningbo/ China
   [SHL_Architects_West-Shanghai-Workers-Cultural-Palace_terrace-view-380x
   260.jpg]

